but that would probably end with everyone screaming at me
summary: Why is there randomly so much hate now for tony stark, loki, and other characters of the like? Ya, they’ve done bad things but...
body: Why is there randomly so much hate now for tony stark, loki, and other characters of the like? Ya, they’ve done bad things but attacking actual people for liking them is worse. I get if there are some annoying fans and you might not like a character and that’s completely valid but making like 6 posts in a row about how much you hate them makes it seem obsessive and like you’re looking for attention. Also can we stop with the civil war discourse already? It’s been almost 3 years they’ve literally had like 5 movies since then, move on.
